## 3. Protocol Economics & Governance

VCTR-SOV is a **Digital Commodity Protocol**, not a financial institution.

### The 1.0% Protocol Constant
Commercial applications utilizing the VCTR-SOV verification layer must remit a **1.0% Protocol Sustainability Constant** to the Genesis Reserve. This fee supports the maintenance of the cryptographic anchor and legal defense of the protocol.

**Genesis Reserve (SOL/SPL):**
`85p7LyG8cG7qk12s3hCwSGVq75AHgQFvrSCfFnCVmeQi`

